|---------|-----------|-----------|
| Primary button fill | Powder Blue 500 | Powder Blue 500 |
| Primary button hover | Powder Blue 600 | Powder Blue 400 |
| Link / text action | Powder Blue 500 | Powder Blue 300 |
| Focus ring | Powder Blue 400 | Powder Blue 400 |
| Page background | white | Powder Blue 950 |
| Sidebar / panel bg | Dusty Taupe 50 | Powder Blue 900 |
| Card background | white | Powder Blue 800 |
| Border (default) | Dusty Taupe 100 | Powder Blue 700 |
| Border (hover/emphasis) | Dusty Taupe 200 | Powder Blue 600 |
| Text primary | Powder Blue 900 | Dusty Taupe 50 |
| Text secondary | Powder Blue 700 | Powder Blue 300 |
| Text tertiary / caption | Dusty Taupe 400 | Powder Blue 600 |

