## Spacing & Radius

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| radius-sm | 4px | Pills, inline tags |
| radius-md | 8px | Inputs, badges, buttons |
| radius-lg | 12px | Cards, panels, drawers |
| gap-xs | 4px | Tight icon gaps |
| gap-sm | 8px | Inline element gaps |
| gap-md | 12px | Component internal gaps |
| gap-lg | 16px | Between components |
| gap-xl | 24px | Section spacing |

---

## Borders

- Default border: `0.5px solid` — barely-there, keeps surfaces light
- Hover/emphasis border: `1px solid`
- Featured/selected card accent: `2px solid` (only exception, e.g. active document card)
- Never use rounded corners with single-sided borders (e.g. `border-left` only). Rounded corners require borders on all sides.

---

## Component Rules

### Buttons
- Primary: Powder Blue 500 fill, white text, radius-md
- Secondary/ghost: transparent bg, 0.5px border, text primary color, radius-md
- Destructive: use red — not defined in this palette, use Tailwind `red-600`
- Icon button: 32×32px, Dusty Taupe 50 bg, radius-md
- No gradients, no shadows on buttons

### Inputs & Search
- Background: Dusty Taupe 50 (light) / Powder Blue 900 (dark)
- Border: 0.5px Dusty Taupe 100
- Focus ring: 2px Powder Blue 400, no border-color change
- Height: 36px, padding 0 12px
- Icon: leading search icon in text-tertiary color

### Cards (document list, history entries)
- Background: white (light) / Powder Blue 800 (dark)
- Border: 0.5px Dusty Taupe 100
- Radius: radius-lg
- Padding: 16px 20px
- Hover: border upgrades to Dusty Taupe 200

### Feature Badges (popover + history)
- Inline-flex, align-items center, gap 5px
- Height: ~24px, padding 3px 10px
- Radius: 100px (pill)
- Font: 12px / 500
- Icon: 13px, leading, from Font Awesome (production) or Tabler (previews)
- Colors: see Feature Color Assignments table above

### History Entries
- Layout: flex row, gap 10px
- Icon square: 20×20px, radius 4px, feature bg color (stop 100), feature icon (stop 800)
- Title: 13px / 500, text-primary, single line with text-overflow ellipsis
- Meta: 12px / 400, text-tertiary — format: `{Feature} · Page {n}`
- Hover: border upgrades, subtle bg tint

### PDF Highlight Overlay
- Vanilla Custard 500 (`#ffee00`) at ~40% opacity
- Rendered as absolute-positioned div over normalized rect coordinates (0–1 ratio relative to page dimensions)
- Must recalculate position on zoom/resize — coordinates are stored normalized, converted to px at render time

### Chat Drawer
- Animates in from the right within the PDF content area (not a full-screen overlay)
- Background: white (light) / Powder Blue 900 (dark)
- Border-left: 0.5px Dusty Taupe 100
- Width: ~360px
- Trigger button: Powder Blue 50 bg, Powder Blue 500 icon

### Sidebar / Page List
- Background: Dusty Taupe 50 (light) / Powder Blue 900 (dark)
- Width: ~56px collapsed, ~180px expanded
- Border-right: 0.5px Dusty Taupe 100

---

## Dark Mode Rules

- Toggle between light and dark — no system default auto-switching
- Backgrounds shift from white → Powder Blue 950/900/800 (deepening hierarchy)
- Text shifts from Powder Blue 900 → Dusty Taupe 50
- Borders shift from Dusty Taupe 100 → Powder Blue 700
- Feature badge colors invert: use stop 800 bg + stop 100 text in dark mode
- Vanilla Custard highlight stays `#ffee00` at ~40% opacity in both modes — it's visible on dark PDF backgrounds too

