## Icon Library

Font Awesome (production). Use `fa-regular` (outline) style by default. `fa-solid` only for active/selected states.

Sizes: 14px inline, 16px default UI, 20px decorative max.

| Context | Icon |
|---------|------|
| Note | `fa-pencil` |
| Translate | `fa-language` |
| Summarize | `fa-wand-magic-sparkles` |
| Chat | `fa-message` |
| Search | `fa-magnifying-glass` |
| Upload | `fa-arrow-up-from-bracket` |
| Bookmark | `fa-bookmark` |
| History panel | `fa-clock-rotate-left` |
| Document | `fa-file-pdf` |
| Page list | `fa-bars` |
| Close / dismiss | `fa-xmark` |

---

## What Not to Do

- No gradients anywhere
- No box-shadows (except 0-spread focus rings)
- No font-weight 600 or 700
- No title case or all-caps text (except 11px section labels)
- No Vanilla Custard 500 in UI — PDF highlights only
- No rounded corners on single-sided borders
- Do not use Dusty Taupe as a feature color — it is structural/neutral only
- Do not add a fourth AI feature color without updating the semantic table above
